    {
      "chinese": "會所為部落的教育訓練、交誼、討論公共事務的場所。多納男性約從16、17歲開始進入會所過夜直到結婚之後才改變。會所領導人負責部落所有軍事活動，其並非貴族世襲方式，而是透過部落長老與會所成員公議推舉而產生。",
      "ab": "siwkayzyo ka pwaikay tacekecekelane ni’ikay boboo kenglringi, mabakabaka sa’avavanita ka sakabaane na ma’aka dwapenga. Thakongadavane na sa’oalay ka syalikay no twamangesalini sika eneme sika pito na cavili. sikyaodro ’ikay siwkayzyo ’isolay pata’athay no sapalanganininga laso baithi. kikay wameamece sikiningi tacekecekelane na sana’a dwape ka, ikamani na talyalalay. matawmanamana sidwape pasilikay tacekecekelane. na maodrange si thabathabae pii ko noameamece ami.",
      "order": "3",
